               <msContents>
                  <summary>Epistles of Paul and Warqat Tergwami</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="227v">1r-227v</locus>
                     <title>Commentary on the Pauline Epistles</title>
                     <note>Romans, fol. 1r-56r; 1 Corinthians, fol. 56r-113r; 2 Corinthians, fol. 113r-132v; Galatians, fol. 132v-143r; Ephesians, fol. 143r-152v; Philippians, fol. 152v-160r; Colossians, fol. 160r-166r; 1 Thessalonians, fol. 166r-170r; 2 Thessalonians, fol. 170r-172v; 1 Timothy, fol. 172v-180r; 2 Timothy, fol. 180r-184v; Titus, fol. 184v-187v; Philemon, fol. 187v-189r; Hebrews, fol. 189r-227v
                        
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="am"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="am">መልእክት ፡ ቀዳማዊ ፡ ኀበ ፡ ሰብአ ፡ ሮሜ ፤ ታሪክ ፡ ይህችን ፡ ሀገር ፡ ብዙ ፡ ጊዜ ፡ ቈጽሮታል ። እምቅድመ ፡ ማየ ፡ አይኅ ፡ አርሳጣጣሊላ ፡ ትባል ፡ ነበረ ፡ ውሉደ ፡ ከይተም ፡ ቢለፍሩባት ፡
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="232r" to="341v">232r-341v</locus>
                     <title>ረድእ ፡ ወመምህር, Book of the master and the disciple by Cyril</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">መገፃዊ ፡ ቡሩክ ፡ እስትጉቡእ ፡ በእንተ ፡ አስተጋብኦ ፡ ዝንቱ ፡ መጽሐፍ ፡ ወውእቱ ፡ ፳ወ፪መብህልት ፡ መምሕር ፡ ወረድእ ፡ ይብቌዕ ፡ እግዚአብሔር ፡ ኪያሁ ፡ ለሰማዒ ፡ ወያርድእ ፡ ገቢረ ፡ በእንተ ፡ መድኃኒተ ፡ ነፍስ ፡ አሜን ፤ መብህልት ፡ ግዕዝት ፡ ይከሥት ፡ በውስቴታ ፡ ፍኖተ ፡ እንተ ፡ ታበጽሕ ፡ ኀበ ፡ ድኂን ፡ እምኃጢት ።
                     </incipit>
                     <note>The colophon erroneously attributes the translation to the reign of Emperor Śarḍa Dengel                        
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
